From 282f84efe246931f096719c5e67f818db5389c70 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Sat, 6 Jun 2026 06:01:50 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat(blog): add blog feature with CMS, public listing, and
 article pages

- supabase/schema_blog.sql: blog_posts table with RLS (anon reads published, auth reads/writes all) + blog-images storage bucket
- src/lib/blog.js: Supabase CRUD for posts, image upload to storage, read time calculation, slugify helper
- src/pages/Blog.jsx: /blog listing page with category filter, post grid, skeleton loading, react-helmet-async SEO
- src/pages/BlogPost.jsx: /blog/:slug article page with react-markdown, JSON-LD schema (Article/FAQ/LocalBusiness), related posts, WhatsApp + copy-link sharing
- src/styles/blog.css: full blog design system (cards, filters, markdown typography, share bar, CMS editor styles)
- src/main.jsx: BrowserRouter + HelmetProvider wrapping site routes (/, /blog, /blog/:slug); admin path unchanged
- src/components/Site.jsx: added Blog link to nav and mobile drawer
- src/admin/AdminApp.jsx: Blog CMS tab with post list (paginated), visual Markdown editor with toolbar, SEO fields, cover image upload, draft/publish workflow

https://claude.ai/code/session_01EHchyXDL4cW4zX3UV5cfXV
